{"tid":661772,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"收到風阿爺要打擊燈神","createTime":"2018-05-12T00:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T01:04:41.000Z","uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed2ffb6487fdb93533155f965c053cb1616c39e","tid":661772,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T00:33:46.000Z","msg":"中證監今召開例行發佈會，中證監表示，部署2018年專項執法行動第一批案件，將集中打擊通過互聯網、自媒體肆意發表證券期貨虛假信息，充當股市「黑嘴」，並從中牟利等嚴重擾亂資本市場信息傳播秩序的違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n中證監集中部署8宗典型案件，主要表現為通過微博、微信等新媒體發布文章，傳播虛假信息；通過股吧等網絡平台，編造不準確信息誤導投資者；網絡大V（獲認證的KOL）提前買入股票，涉嫌「搶帽子」（即春江鴨）交易的行為等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180511/58180258 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58180258%20&d=30i5dmQtolhkj2cGjx6Lsk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4f3314be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58180258%20&h=07cb490b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180511/58180258 </a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62e03912c8fd5459a34beecadd572344145fdc1","tid":661772,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df55d4e9d4b7f4d14f810f766e92cabdd597abb2","tid":661772,"uid":90,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"媽咪麵馬化雲老貓每天被打<br />\n沈大師燒生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32f255ff4d7fb5d8262543dc0ac2acfc3575f90","tid":661772,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df55d4e9d4b7f4d14f810f766e92cabdd597abb2","tid":661772,"uid":90,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"re